               <msContents>
                  <summary>The first line informs us that the subject is the livelihood of orphans, who may have had some of their property seized from them. If this were a petition or official document, we would expect an address to an official and a very large amount of text lost to the left. More likely, perhaps, is a private letter voicing such concerns.</summary>
